title: Don Mottin - Stage Hypnosis Training Course
description:
If you want to learn what to do in a stage show and why you should do it, this tutorial DVD is what you 
are looking for! Don Mottin shares a stage show that he performed, then stops the show at that point to 
tell you what he did and explains his reasoning.  Whether you are a beginner or a seasoned 
professional, you will find this information valuable to your performance.
